      "title": "HOME - AGDATA",
      "description": "As the most trusted provider of data management, analytics, and market program management, we help our clients make more informed decisions.",
      "text_excerpt": "HOME - AGDATA\nPlay Video\nPlay Video\nSolutions\nData Management\nMarketing Program Management\nMarket Intelligence\nTrait License Management\nMarkets\nCrop Inputs\nAnimal Health\nSpecialty\nRetail\nCompany\nOverview\nLeadership\nCareers\nResources\nVideos\nCase Studies\nBlog\nContact\nMAKE SMARTER DATA-DRIVEN DECISIONS\nWith data services at the core – surrounded by an extensible array of streamlined software solutions – our unified platform represents over three decades of innovation and expertise in the agriculture, crop protection, specialty chemical and animal health industries.\nPlay Video\nFINDING NEW WAYS TO OPTIMIZE PROGRAMS\nAs the most trusted provider of data management, analytics, and market program management in North America, we help our clients make better informed decisions and run more efficient, accurate programs.\nPlay Video\nSOLUTIONS TO GROW, IMPROVE, AND PROTECT\nManufacturers, distributors, and retailers of all sizes rely on our sophisticated data-centric approach to improve the ROI on sales and marketing initiatives, build stronger relationships and protect market share.\nPlay Video\nData Management\nA comprehensive set of data management services that enable supply chain visibility and informed decision-making across the entire enterprise.\nLearn More\nMarketing Program Management\nIntegrated planning, calculation, fulfillment and analysis functions to help maximize the performance of marketing programs while minimizing execution risk.\nLearn More\nMarket Intelligence\nA data processing and analytics solution for the Canadian crop and animal health markets that combines supply chain data with market survey data into accurate, reliable insights.\nLearn More\nTrait License Management\nEverything seed manufacturers need to protect and monetize their intellectual property, including grower licensing, compliance management and reporting.\nLearn More\nMarkets\nCrop Inputs\nAnimal Health\nSpecialty\nStatistics\nProgram Funds Managed Annually\nData Collection from North American Distributers & Retailers\nSales Transactions Processed Annually\nResults We've Delivered\nCase Study\nCorteva Agriscience™\nCorteva Agriscience™ offers grower purchase programs across Canada for their seed and crop protection products.\nLearn more\nCase Study\nPet King Brands\nPet King Brands was looking for a way to manage their data at the clinic and retail level to help them develop insights and grow their market share.\nLearn more\nLet's Get Started\nAGDATA\n© 2025 AGDATA. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.  |\nPRIVACY POLICY"
